data.text:
List of famous athletes from Turkey, listed alphabetically with photos when available. Turkey has seen some very talented athletes over the years, many of who have gone on to represent their country in the Olympics. These are some of the best Turkish athletes of all time, so if you're a native of Turkey and are aspiring to compete in sports professionally then these are people you should look up to. If you're searching for a particular popular athlete from Turkey then you can use the "search" box to find who you're looking for.

Use every item on this list for yours, from Can Bartu to Serdar Aziz.

This list answers the questions, "Who are the greatest Turkish athletes?" and "Which athletes are from Turkey?"

You can click on the names of these legendary athletes of Turkey in order to get more information about each one.
